{"tid":567084,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 花椒油 (帶麻)","createTime":"2018-02-20T14:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T06:45:15.000Z","uid":74981,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fc3cd87809757aa558702b81307abfa826729faa","tid":567084,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s9.postimg.org/o517289qn/20180220_205021.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs9.postimg.org%2Fo517289qn%2F20180220_205021.jpg&h=bcdd9c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>影片如下:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ybpcEdVXshY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FybpcEdVXshY&d=AIjEl420fhfeWz7y5SIGAQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=17ae3aff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ybpcEdVXshY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>材料: </ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n- 2茶匙麻椒<br />\n<br />\n- 6茶匙青花椒<br />\n<br />\n- 油適量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花椒基本上分為滷水用花椒同煮川菜用花椒. 煮川菜用既花椒有青花椒, 大紅袍等等. 花椒煮出黎既野唔麻, 但咬爛左係個口入面就會麻. 如果要煮出黎既野有麻味, 就要用麻椒.<br />\n<br />\n現在分享下本癲狗麻味花椒油既做法, 家裡常備一樽, 可隨時用黎煮下麻婆豆腐, 雞煲, 酸辣粉, 甚至溝潮州辣椒油點燒買, 都有畫龍點精既功效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 將2茶匙麻椒, 6茶匙青花椒入樽<br />\n<br />\n2. 燒滾適量既油, 攤到溫度跌到一半以上, 遂少遂少淋落D花椒度, 避免油溫過熱令花椒燶, 失去香味同產生苦味.<br />\n<br />\n3. 花椒同油浸一晚, 完成. 如果等唔切, 浸半個鐘都已經香香地, 夠拎黎煮送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下期再同大家分享多D麻辣菜式既做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a674c752f2749811acbe826d70eb5b6ba450d50","tid":567084,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39220bc5466406e9441a2e8fc47cd77befbc3f8e","tid":567084,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a674c752f2749811acbe826d70eb5b6ba450d50","tid":567084,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"衲dee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b2386f629535f3c8dfd057d968eec0193c06e9","tid":567084,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"好冇冇咁辣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6945363bc68c60ac5dda3d0b7876d780cdc290c","tid":567084,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:22:21.000Z","msg":"正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd78377e19eddacfeb98915064d4c9eaf9f8b5c","tid":567084,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"鍾意麻辣<br />\n留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280167fb1e00710a68b72168d99322c6bdced339","tid":567084,"uid":6439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"今晚食狗肉煲加料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225a1758c0075c2f21faa75e8d7b18a485333bde","tid":567084,"uid":41855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"留名試做先"},{"pid":"94e278f6964f1c8827bcebcb8597827494e13760","tid":567084,"uid":12158,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:33:10.000Z","msg":"有花椒油賣喎師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企大大支喺度。"},{"pid":"e3c090d22c3c96ea798d0656d8a2dfc0c82d0ec5","tid":567084,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\